# Dialog & sheet preferences

Dialogs and sheets must match the product-card **bubble** aesthetic — soft, rounded, floating. Prefer editing shared `Dialog` / `Sheet` primitives so every modal inherits the look.

## Shape & surface

- Container: `rounded-[32px]` (sheets: `rounded-t-[32px]` / side sheets with matching large radii)
- White surface, soft `shadow-xl` — **no** hairline rings, borders, or bordered footer strips
- Generous padding (`p-5`–`p-6`); airy spacing, not dense shadcn defaults
- Overlay: soft darken + light blur (`bg-black/20`, `backdrop-blur-sm`)

## Controls

- Close button: circular (`size-9 rounded-full`), soft grey fill (`bg-zinc-100`), like the product-card `+`
- Primary / secondary actions: **pill** buttons (`h-11 rounded-full px-5`)
- Inputs in dialogs: pill (`rounded-full`), soft fill (`bg-zinc-100`), no hard border
- List rows / options: soft bubbles (`rounded-[28px]`, muted fill), circular trailing `+` / check — not flat `rounded-lg` menu rows

## Patterns

- Use shared `@/components/ui/dialog` (and `sheet`) rather than one-off modal chrome
- Avoid default shadcn “box” look: small radius, `ring-1`, muted footer bar with `border-t`
- Reference: product card (`rounded-[32px]`–`[40px]`, pill price, circular `+`)

```tsx
// ❌ BAD — sharp default dialog
className="rounded-xl ring-1 ring-foreground/10 p-4"

// ✅ GOOD — bubble dialog
className="rounded-[32px] bg-white p-6 shadow-xl"
```
